e":"2021-04-06T19:49:59.000Z","msg":"台灣<br />\nibizaink <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/IBIZAINK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FIBIZAINK&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=95c69d5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/IBIZAINK</a><br />\n你好紋身 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/htstaipei\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhtstaipei&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=811914ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/htstaipei</a><br />\nendless_tattoo 無盡紋身<br />\n紅貓體啄 - BloodCat Tattoo <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bloodcattattoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbloodcattattoo&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=37ba6dad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bloodcattattoo</a><br />\njoshlintattoo<br />\nVJ TATTOO [FB]<br />\nLotus Tatoo - Ki ( ig:KI210 ) ( <a href=\"http://www.lotustattoo.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lotustattoo.hk&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=4769414d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lotustattoo.hk</a> ) ( 日式, 很好的 by 文仔 )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國外<br />\nivana tattoo art [USA](水彩)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Ivana-Tattoo-Art/208943449123095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpages%2FIvana-Tattoo-Art%2F208943449123095&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=13664ad5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pages/Ivana-Tattoo-Art/208943449123095</a><br />\nbenvolt [USA] (Geometric)<br />\ndr_woo_ssc [USA]<br />\nsashaunisex [Russia] (水彩style,個人認為超靚)<br />\nwoo_tattooer [Korea]<br />\ntattooistdoy [Korea]<br />\nseoeonmo [Korea] <a href=\"http://seoeonmo.blog.me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fseoeonmo.blog.me&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=8727599e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://seoeonmo.blog.me</a><br />\ndotstolines [Berlin] (線條圖案)<br />\nNiki [Sweden] ( 全世界Black and Grey最好的, 文仔認為 ) ( ig :niki23gtr )<br />\nAscension Tattoo [USA] ( Best Tattoo Studio in Orlando for 9 years ) <a href=\"http://ascensiontattoo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fascensiontattoo.com&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=496eea32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ascensiontattoo.com</a><br />\ngakkinx [ Japan ] ( Black work, Japanese )<br />\nslavastarkov [ Russia ] ( 雖然系戰鬥民族, 但做傳統日式好靚)<br />\n9<br />\n3<br />\n#2<br />\n雙目燈形<br />\n&bull;<br />\n4 個月前<br />\n保養紋身 by 皮兒初為瓏夫<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum11.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CO&amp;message=5699139&amp;page=24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum11.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCO%26message%3D5699139%26page%3D24&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=f6d500fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum11.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CO&amp;message=5699139&amp;page=24</a><br />\n<br />\n睇黎好多巴絲都唔識保養紋身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每隔幾頁就有人問一次<br />\n作為喜愛紋身既我分享下<br />\n大部份人紋完之後紋身師都會用保鮮紙之類幫你包好個紋身<br />\n其實都系只系for你番屋企/紋完果幾個鐘<br />\n因為岩岩紋完你傷口仲好新鮮<br />\n要黎保護紋身同埋等d血/墨水唔好揩到周圍都系<br />\n通常隔2-3小時就會拆番落黎(如果用吸血紙除外 吸血紙我再講)<br />\n千萬唔好包實紋身一日以上<br />\n見過有人紋完包實幾日發炎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己又痕又痛之余仲要整花個圖我諗大家都唔想架系咪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拆左保鮮紙後你個紋身應該系好濕潤(血水加墨水)<br />\n呢個時候用凍水衝一衝 輕輕捽一捽表面就ok<br />\n之後可以用紋身師比你既藥膏/凡士林搽個紋身<br />\n唔好用重香味既body lotion 因為會刺激傷口 美白果d更加唔好 你都唔想紋完又幫你漂到淡哂色架<br />\n<br />\nFor第一次紋身既人<br />\n<br />\n流程<br />\n1. wtsapp/fb/dm/email約傾圖<br />\n2. 準備好自己想紋乜去到同個師傅講紋幾大、紋邊度<br />\n3. 師傅會話大慨點紋同大慨咩價錢，約時間紋，俾訂<br />\n4. 紋之前幾日有啲師傅會俾圖你，睇你有冇野改 / 有啲師傅會當日先俾圖，然後再傾，傾好就紋<br />\n5. 紋完post圖，同準備下個紋身"},{"pid":"033935aa00e0fe12b384861383a81f386757d0f0","tid":2478093,"uid":27190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19